enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
sentences: The third workshop under the Dialogue on long-term cooperative action to address climate change by enhancing implementation of the Convention (Decision 1/CP.11) began on Wednesday morning.
The workshop was co-facilitated by Sandea de Wet (South Africa) and Howard Bamsey (Australia).
UNFCCC Executive Secretary Yvo de Boer presented an overview of progress and activities under the Dialogue.
SBSTA Chair Kumarsingh recalled key messages from the previous day's in-session workshops, stressing the strategic importance of energy efficiency.
